text: Check out the new official poster for Star Wars: The Force Awakens featuring Harrison Ford (Han Solo), Carrie Fisher (Princess Leia), Daisy Ridley (Rey), John Boyega (Finn), and a masked Adam Driver as the evil Kylo Ren.
